  "description": "Modal resonators on all voices with character pushed to 0.82–0.92 (near-maximum inharmonicity). At this character value, the Bessel function zero ratios are stretched toward metallic plate behavior, moving from circular drumhead physics toward gong and cymbal acoustic territory. Large reverb space. The 8 Bessel mode stacks ring like a struck metal plate orchestra.",
